Scenario RAM freed by <code>end()</code> Active TLS (HTTPS) connection ~45 KB Active plain HTTP connection ~5–10 KB <p>Call <code>client.end()</code> after a burst of requests if your sketch enters a long idle period:</p> <pre><code>// Burst of requests
for (int i = 0; i &lt; 10; i++) {
    client.get("/data").getBody("v", &amp;val);
    // ... process val
}

client.end(); // free ~45KB of TLS buffers
delay(60 * 1000); // sleep for 1 minute
</code></pre>
